#: ../../content/applications/hr/appraisals/goals.rst:77
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon **only** "
"appears when the mouse hovers over the top-right corner of a goal card."
